{"tid":1974270,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女星素顏照公開！孫藝珍、潤娥比上妝更美，「最強肉體」女偶像暗沈黑眼圈嚇壞人！","createTime":"2020-04-15T17:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:41:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90f5a50944d2e9d50e0e8759a1c21ad3f0a9ba5d","tid":1974270,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"韓國女星們的好皮膚是大家都認證的，即使在高清鏡頭下看起來水嫩又白皙，但是當她們卸妝後也是這麼無瑕嗎？今天來為大家搜集韓國女星們的素顏照，漂亮姊姊孫藝珍和潤娥都是公認的比上妝更美，而有最強肉體稱號的女偶像，竟然意外膚色暗沈嚇壞大家？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>IU 吃可愛長大的國民妹妹</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jdqVhUJLZPQq3gbLDUKc8A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/2de99360-7eee-11ea-bfff-65cc0fff8d73\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjdqVhUJLZPQq3gbLDUKc8A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F2de99360-7eee-11ea-bfff-65cc0fff8d73&h=3321c998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即使素顏有點黑眼圈，IU的好膚質依舊讓人羨慕！<br />\n<br />\n有國民妹妹稱號的IU不只歌唱實力超強、演出的戲劇作品也是每部都引發高討論度，母胎美人的她素顏照看起來雖然有點黑眼圈，但是白皙又水嫩的膚質依舊，就算是高清鏡頭看起來還是超美的！而她之前透露自己會在家使用牛奶來自製面膜，維持白嫩的豆腐美肌！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>孫藝珍 漂亮姊姊素顏也無懈可擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n因為和玄彬演出《愛的迫降》再度爆紅的孫藝珍，真的是大家認證的漂亮姊姊代表。今年38歲的她素顏看起來年紀更小，甚至還被化妝師爆料膚質好到不需要粉底！而她的獨門保養秘訣就是每天會使用檸檬水來洗臉，使肌膚更加白皙！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V0JyQpHipqKDdB7dlZjWeg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/2ddaed60-7eee-11ea-bdbb-3517f5d77957\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FV0JyQpHipqKDdB7dlZjWeg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F2ddaed60-7eee-11ea-bdbb-3517f5d77957&h=3ced4bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然38歲了，孫藝珍的肌膚依然好得像少女！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>潤娥 素顏依舊是門面擔當</strong><br />\n<br />\n少女時代出道的潤娥擁有清秀的鄰家女孩臉蛋，即使不斷有強勁對手，她依舊是許多人心目中永遠的初戀臉！而她的素顏更是幾乎和上妝完全沒有差異，因為保養得宜所以平常就幾乎都是清透的淡妝為主！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u8nW2PwBwLpA5ViOG88vUQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/2dd484c0-7eee-11ea-bd9e-dd4458bb7f64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fu8nW2PwBwLpA5ViOG88vUQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F2dd484c0-7eee-11ea-bd9e-dd4458bb7f64&h=f03fdf39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潤娥的素顏和妝後幾乎0差異，受到大家認證！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>子瑜 黑眼圈擋不住最強美貌</strong><br />\n<br />\n台灣人的驕傲子瑜一出道就因為高顏值受到矚目，也曾多次入選全球百大美女榜單！年紀輕輕的她其實素顏沒有太大差異，只是因為暗沈顯得有些疲憊。而她之前也被拍到，私下會使用面具來加強面膜的保養效果，達到事半功倍的效率！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TtdFkHbcWfTGOchuV.J2nQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/2df245f0-7eee-11ea-8ce3-3364d7741c0d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTtdFkHbcWfTGOchuV.J2nQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F2df245f0-7eee-11ea-8ce3-3364d7741c0d&h=5cdcd7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEtNWWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEtNWWR.jpg&h=78899fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mF6jN3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmF6jN3B.jpg&h=c6e95610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n子瑜卸妝後看起來依舊清純，只是感覺有點疲憊。<br />\n<strong><br />\n雪炫 最強肉體素顏超驚人</strong><br />\n<br />\n擁有前凸後翹的好身材，雪炫一出道就讓全韓國的男性為她瘋狂！螢光幕前亮眼的她之前登上綜藝節目秀出素顏，沒想到意外看起來膚色黝黑又暗沉，讓大家都嚇了一跳，而她自己也承認對素顏不是很有自信，需要多保養呢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GEMtxwKp1uVrHz0Mr2nd7g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/2dddac80-7eee-11ea-bbff-9be769d45d77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGEMtxwKp1uVrHz0Mr2nd7g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F2dddac80-7eee-11ea-bbff-9be769d45d77&h=98b55e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪炫卸妝後的暗沈模樣讓不少粉絲嚇壞！"},{"pid":"337dff27429e92e5f07f51f181253d265ce6b24d","tid":1974270,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"求入嚟支持一下黃色音樂圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同一位挪威朋友寫咗首歌送比咁多位同路人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fnKgJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fnKgJS</a>"},{"pid":"fefe3eaa6138b24ccf28dccf97747afcd844fe02","tid":1974270,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"337dff27429e92e5f07f51f181253d265ce6b24d","tid":1974270,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"求入嚟支持一下黃色音樂圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同一位挪威朋友寫咗首歌送比咁多位同路人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fnKgJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fnKgJS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"WA多謝多謝"},{"pid":"f744b711c53e862314f6b95cd46dfcc09690b41a","tid":1974270,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fefe3eaa6138b24ccf28dccf97747afcd844fe02","tid":1974270,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"337dff27429e92e5f07f51f181253d265ce6b24d","tid":1974270,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"